  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/RumalKhan" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Rumal Khan</a>
  </h1>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/RumalKhan">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">RumalKhan</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Labour candidate in Portsmouth North for the UK 2017 General Election. Currently the candidate in Nelson Ward for the May 2018 local elections. <a href="/hashtag/rumal4nelson?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>rumal4nelson</b></a></p>

    rumalkhan.org/2017/05/06/sta

      </div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Many thanks to everyone who attended the Stand Up To Racism event yesterday.       <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="embed-code-container">

  <form class="t1-form">

    <div class="embed-destination-wrapper">
      <div class="embed-overlay embed-overlay-spinner"><div class="embed-overlay-content"></div></div>

        <div class="embed-include-parent-tweet">

    </div>
  </form>
